articles.title: Harris’ proposals would increase the national debt, but Trump’s would add even more, study finds - CNN
articles.description: Both Vice President Kamala Harris and former President Donald Trump are rolling out an ever-growing list of promises to voters – from making housing and health care more affordable to supporting manufacturers to providing tax relief to millions of Americans.
